  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is an observational study aiming to identify and validate biomarkers (including imaging
      and clinical descriptors) for chronic obstructive pulmonary disease (COPD), cardiovascular
      disease (CVD) and lung cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
